Hey guys   What I do to remove steering wheels is to drill two holes oppisite 
from each other under the horn button then tap them and use a crows foot 
puller to remove the wheel being careful of the threads on the shaft. .  heat and 
penatrating oil are you friends here . later and have fun  Mark Dearing
